6.	Crear Workbook para visualización
  ●	Portal → Monitor → Workbooks → New → Add → Add query. 
    1.	Estado de la VM (Heartbeat)
      ○	Consulta:
        Heartbeat
        | summarize LastSeen = max(TimeGenerated)
      ○	Log Analytics Workspace: Cargar todas las suscripciones (Tu Log Analytics Workspace)
      ○	Visualización: Set by query (te lo muestra como “Grid”)
      ○	Done editing
      ○	Save
      ○	Title: wb-vmmon-01
      ○	Subscription: Tu subscripción
      ○	Resource group: rg-vmmon-setup
      ○	Location: (Europe) Spain Central
Captura: “06_01.wb-vmmon-01(heartbeat).png”
    2.	CPU (Performance Counter)
      ○	Consulta:
        Perf
        | where CounterName == "% Processor Time"
        | summarize AvgCPU = avg(CounterValue) by bin(TimeGenerated, 5m)
      ○	Log Analytics Workspace: Cargar todas las suscripciones (Tu Log Analytics Workspace)
      ○	Visualización: Line chart
      ○	Done editing
      ○	Save
Captura: “06_02.wb-vmmon-01(cpu).png”

    3.	Memoria disponible (Performance Counters)
      ○	Consulta:
        Perf
        | where CounterName == "Available Bytes"
        | extend AvailableMB = todouble(CounterValue) / 1000000.0
        | summarize AvgAvailableMB = avg(AvailableMB) by bin(TimeGenerated, 5m)
        | extend AvgAvailableMB = round(AvgAvailableMB, 2)
        | render timechart with (ytitle="Available (MBytes)")
      ○	Log Analytics Workspace: Cargar todas las suscripciones (Tu Log Analytics Workspace)
      ○	Visualización: Line chart
      ○	Done editing
      ○	Save
Captura: “06_03.wb-vmmon-01(memory).png”

    4.	Espacio en disco (Performance Counters)
      ○	Consulta:
        Perf
        | where CounterName == "% Free Space"
        | summarize AvgFree = avg(CounterValue) by InstanceName
      ○	Log Analytics Workspace: Cargar todas las suscripciones (Tu Log Analytics Workspace)
      ○	Visualización: Bar chart
      ○	Done editing
      ○	Save
Captura: “06_04.wb-vmmon-01(disk).png”

    5.	Eventos críticos y warnings
      ○	Consulta:
        Event
        | where EventID in (4624, 4625)
        | summarize Count = count() by Status = case(EventID == 4624, "Correctos", "Fallidos")
      ○	Log Analytics Workspace: Cargar todas las suscripciones (Tu Log Analytics Workspace)
      ○	Visualización: Pie chart
      ○	Done editing
      ○	Save
Captura:  “06_05.wb-vmmon-01(events).png”

