7.2. Alerta inicio de sesión fallidos
  ●	Portal → Log Analytics Workspace → law-vmmon-setup → Monitoring → Alerts → Create → Alert rule
    ○	Scope: law-vmmon-setup (al crearlo desde el menú de log analytics workspace se autocompleta)
    ○	Condition: Custom log search
      ■	Query type: Aggregated logs
      ■	Search query:
        Event
        | where TimeGenerated > ago(5m)
        | where EventID == 4625
        | summarize fails = count() by Computer
        | where fails >= 5
      ■	Measure: Table rows
      ■	Aggregation type: Count
      ■	Aggregation granularity: 5 minutes
      ■	Resource ID column: Don't split
      ■	Threshold type: Static
      ■	Operator: Greater than
      ■	Threshold value: 0
      ■	Frequency of evaluation: 5 minutes
      ■	Estimated monthly cost $1.50 (USD) 
      ■	Advanced options
      ■	Number of violations: 1
      ■	Evaluation period: 5 minutes (1 aggregated points)
      ■	Override query time range: 5 minutes
Captura: “07_02_01.alert-vmmon-law-critical-events(condition).png”
    ○	Actions
      ■	Action group name: ag-vmmon-alerts
Captura: “07_02_02.alert-vmmon-law-critical-events(actions).png”
    ○	Details
